<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='363337' id='t-363337'>there's no way I can focus on the balls.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='365267' id='t-365267'>I'm going to drop them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='366473' id='t-366473'>Now in life, and in meditation,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='369115' id='t-369115'>there'll be times when the focus
