<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='384324' id='t-384324'>and things just become a sort
of little bit like this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='386920' id='t-386920'>Of course in meditation --</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388609' id='t-388609'>(Snores)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='389634' id='t-389634'>we're going to end up falling asleep.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391443' id='t-391443'>So we're looking for a balance,
a focused relaxation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='394169' id='t-394169'>where we can allow thoughts to come and go</span>
