</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423041' id='t-423041'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='424073' id='t-424073'>You know, this is crazy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425414' id='t-425414'>We do this all the time,
