<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='437200' id='t-437200'>But what do you do every 20, 30 seconds?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440737' id='t-440737'>(Mumbling)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442642' id='t-442642'>It does hurt.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='443835' id='t-443835'>And we reinforce the storyline, right?</span>
